OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be dry with
OL,6,Fplenty of sunshine. Remaining dry this
OL,7,Fafternoon with some spells of sunshine
OL,8,Fbut Argyll and the Isles may cloud
OL,9,Fover for a while. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry and
OL,12,Fclear with some patchy frost. Clouding
OL,13,Fover from the south in the early hours
OL,14,Fwith a few showers spreading northeast.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FA rather cloudy day with
OL,17,Foccasional rain in the morning, this
OL,18,Fbecoming mostly confined to Argyll by
OL,19,Fafternoon. Chance of some brighter
OL,20,Fspells in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
