OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FCloudy with rain on Thursday, becoming
OL,7,Fdrier from the west later. Dry and
OL,8,Fbright on Friday and Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
